le=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到盐城市第一人民医院（急诊六楼）招标采购中心投标报名，投标报名时间2018年&nbsp;8&nbsp;月27 &nbsp;日至2018年&nbsp;8&nbsp;月&nbsp;31&nbsp;日；联系人：王主任，联系方式：0515-88507786。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">5.&nbsp;本项目采用竞争性谈判。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">6、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">7、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-88508906。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">时间：2018年&nbsp;8&nbsp;月&nbsp;27&nbsp;日</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2018-08-27\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2018-08-27\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'18ce945412d52d5d\',\n  \'views\' => \'610\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844842');
