2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中 标 价：9.1万元</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">四、南区地下一层、地下二层公共区域更换LED灯项目</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中标单位：无锡邦得光电科技有限公司</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中 标 价：14.9730万元</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">五、北区供应室蒸汽凝结水回收项目</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中标单位：江苏通海工业设备安装有限公司</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中 标 价：13.2万元</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">六、北区智慧用电安全隐患监管服务系统采购与安装项目</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中标单位：盐城平安智慧电气工程有限公司</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">中 标 价：17.5230万元</span></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">为体现公开、公平、公正的原则，特此公告三天。如有疑问请与盐城市第一人民医院监察室联系，电话0515-88508906。</span></p><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2018年7月14日</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2018-07-14\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2018-07-14\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'ae999d7ea0f4c991\',\n  \'views\' => \'799\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844850');
